<note n="0685009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685009">上＝之一【明】</note>
<note n="0685010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685010">（摩訶…善覺）十四字作本文【三】</note>
<note n="0685011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685011">塠＝搥【宋】，堆【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0685012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685012">唱＝倡【三】</note>
<note n="0685013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685013">伎＝<g ref="#CB05718">𠆸</g>【宋】【元】，妓【明】＊</note>
<note n="0685014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685014">杖＝仗【三】</note>
<note n="0685015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0685015">矟＝槊【三】＊</note>
<note n="0686001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686001">車＝連【明】</note>
<note n="0686002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686002">樂＝喜【三】</note>
<note n="0686003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686003">暉＝翬【三】</note>
<note n="0686004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686004">合十指＝<choice><orig><g ref="#CB00566">䠒</g>跪</orig><reg type="通用詞">胡跪</reg></choice>合【宋】，胡跪合【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0686005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686005">惓＝倦【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0686006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686006">座＝坐【三】</note>
<note n="0686007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686007">得無＝無得【三】</note>
<note n="0686008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686008">已＝以【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0686009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0686009">痒＝癢【明】</note>
<note n="0687001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0687001">裹＝裏【明】＊</note>
<note n="0687002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0687002">於＝初【宋】</note>
</p>
